data.description: Welcome to this stunning modern home, where design meets functionality. Step into a bright living space, perfect for gatherings. Expansive windows bathe the home in natural light. The sleek kitchen boasts high-end appliances and a large island. The master suite offers luxury with a spacious bedroom, walk-in closet, and spa-like ensuite. Tile flooring, laundry room, and a 2-car garage enhance convenience. Outdoors, enjoy landscaped yards, a deck, and a vast covered patio for Texas evenings. In Lindale's Woodland Creek, relish large homes, yards, and top-rated schools. Embrace style and comfort here.
